  "html": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Day 23 - Kanji Practice</span></p><div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Please download today&#39;s kanji practice here: <a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"../../pdfs/week_05/day_23/Kanji_Practice_Day_23.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Kanji Practice Day 23.pdf</a></p><p>Practising writing kanji every day is a very important exercise to help you learn quickly. If you have any questions you can always ask other students and teachers in the community <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p><p>Refer back to the <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/manage/courses/731527/contents/18333471\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Week 5 - Kanji lesson</a> to watch how to do the correct stroke order for 食, 飲, 買.&nbsp;</p></div>",
